             depos'd, that the Wood was bought at his House publickly, and some of it appear'd to be damaged, and therefore there was Allowance made for it. 
               <persName id="t17240226-64-person319">
                  Thomas 
                  Jones 
               <interp inst="t17240226-64-person319" type="surname" value="Jones"></interp>
